The BigQuery Service Account associated with your project requires access to this encryption key. i.e. projects/{project}/locations/{location}/keyRings/{key_ring}/cryptoKeys/{cryptoKey}. See https://cloud.google.com/bigquery/docs/customer-managed-encryption for more information.
